+## Qwen Added Memories
+- The task is to refactor the ShenYu infrastructure modules to centralize infrastructure dependencies. I've developed:
+
+1. Created new module: shenyu-infra-common with:
+   - Constants for module naming (ShenyuModuleConstants, InfraConstants)
+   - Infrastructure parent properties class (InfraParentProperties)
+   - Conditional annotations for sync infrastructure (@ConditionOnSyncEtcd, @ConditionOnSyncNacos)
+   - Condition implementations for the annotations
+
+2. Created consolidated modules for infrastructure:
+   - shenyu-infra-redis with RedisProperties and RedisConnectionFactory
+   - shenyu-infra-nacos with NacosConfig and NacosACMConfig classes (both with builder patterns)
+   - shenyu-infra-etcd with EtcdConfig and EtcdClient
+
+3. Updated the main infra module pom.xml to include the new modules
+
+The remaining work includes:
+1. Modifying pom.xml files in dependent modules to use new infrastructure dependencies
+2. Updating imports in related modules to use new locations
+3. Removing duplicate classes from original locations (admin-listener, sync-data modules)
